Decorator Design pattern is used in questions like coffe machines
It is the design pattern that have "has a" and "is a" both used.
Their is always one base class and have several decorator layers to increase the features of the base class.
In the Example:
            VegDelight, Margherita and Farmhouse "Is a" relation with BasePizza.
            Topping Decorator have  "has a" relation with BasePizza.
            ExtraCheese and Mushroom "Is a" relation with Topping Decorator
